			<div class="article-correspondence layout-item fill-pattern-light">
		<div class="layout-item-intro">
			<h2>Correspondence</h2>
			<a class="xsmall link-alt" href="https://www.thesunmagazine.org/letter-to-the-editor">Write a Letter to the Editor&nbsp;&#9656;</a>
		</div>

		<div id="article-correspondences" class="correspondences correspondences-collapsed">
								<div class="block-correspondence" id="2751">
		<blockquote class="quote-2">
			<p>I appreciated this passage from Sy Safransky&rsquo;s &ldquo;<a href="/article/1736">Where the Parking Lot Is Now</a>&rdquo; [April 1996]: &ldquo;The back-to-the-land movement, antinuclear marches, civil-rights protests, psychedelics, Eastern mysticism, natural foods, feminism, environmentalism &mdash; we knew these were connected somehow, and not just by a <em>Woodstock</em> soundtrack.&rdquo; It reminded me of one of my favorite Einstein stories. Here it is, in the words of Dr. Ernst Jackh:</p>

<p>&ldquo;As we were going in to dinner, I asked Professor Einstein: &lsquo;Would you agree that it is no mere chance that your theory of relativity, Professor Freud&rsquo;s psychoanalysis, the League of Nations and its World Court, and other phenomena of our time have developed together: that they are all an expression of the same revolutionary phase through which the contemporary world is passing?&rsquo;</p>

<p>&ldquo;Professor Einstein looked at me and said nothing for a moment, and then, &lsquo;This synthetic vision is new to me. Let me think it over.&rsquo; During dinner I watched him, and I noticed that he was eating and drinking nothing, but was staring in front of him and meditating. After dinner, he came up to me and said, &lsquo;You are quite right: I endorse your holism.&rsquo;&nbsp;&rdquo;</p>

<p>And I endorse Safransky&rsquo;s holism. These things <em>are</em> connected, and we seem to be heading into a revolutionary phase of some kind as we approach the new millennium. It will be interesting indeed.</p>
							<p class="quote-2-author">Jim Rennie<br>Diamond Bar, California</p>
					</blockquote>
	</div>

					</div>

			</div>
    
		<div class="article-correspondence-cta">
		<div class="cta cta-l1" data-url="https://www.thesunmagazine.org/letter-to-the-editor">
			<div class="cta-intro">
				<h5 class="cta-title alt-ff">Thinking about writing us a letter?</h5>
				<p class="cta-text">Give in to the temptation. We love getting mail. <br><span class="xsmall">(Of course, we reserve the right to edit.)</span></p>
			</div>
			<a href="https://www.thesunmagazine.org/letter-to-the-editor" class="cta-button b b-4 b-padding-tight small" data-label="Write Us A Letter!">Write Us A Letter!</a>
		</div>
	</div>
	

